Update 250

What follows are the changes visible in the data files for update 250.

THIS SECTION IS IN BETA! Not all changes are detected yet.

Additions

New skills

SKILLDescription
Charged PigA unique combat style for extraordinary swine. (You can place both Pig and Charged Pig abilities on your Charged Pig ability bar.)
Flower ArrangementThe art of arranging flowers so that they evoke strong emotions.
Nature AppreciationThe ability to study nature and find inner peace and contentment. Even the most hardened warriors need the ability to appreciate nature.
